Package: geocodeR
Title: Australian Address Matching and Geocoding with G-NAF
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kyle",
           family = "Haynes",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kyle@kylehaynes.com.au")
Description: Provides functions for matching and geocoding Australian addresses 
    against the Geocoded National Address File (G-NAF). Includes fuzzy string 
    matching, address normalization, and a Shiny application for interactive 
    address geocoding and visualization.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/KyleHaynes/au.address.match
BugReports: https://github.com/KyleHaynes/au.address.match/issues
